# MiOS — Cline Rules

Read `AI.md` in this directory for the complete architecture, laws, and provider index.

## Project

MiOS is a bootc-based immutable workstation OS on Fedora Rawhide. One OCI image covers all roles.
The root filesystem is STRICTLY read-only at runtime — never suggest `dnf install` on the deployed host.

## Critical rules

### kargs.d TOML — only this format is valid:
```toml
kargs = ["key=value", "flag"]
```
Never: `[kargs]` section header · `delete =` · `kargs.append =` · `[[kargs]]`

### Bash
- `VAR=$((VAR + 1))` always — never `((VAR++))` (exits 1 when result=0, kills script under `set -e`)
- `set -euo pipefail` required in all scripts
- Never `dnf install kernel` inside the container; never `--squash-all` on `podman build`

### GNOME
- Never `GTK_THEME=Adwaita:dark` → use `ADW_DEBUG_COLOR_SCHEME=prefer-dark`
- `xorgxrdp-glamor` only (not bare `xorgxrdp`)

### Immutable OS invariants
- All system config in `system_files/` — no top-level overlay directories
- Never `mkdir /var/...` in scripts — use `tmpfiles.d`
- Never `semodule -i` at build time — stage in `/usr/share/selinux/packages/`
- Never `dnf install` at runtime on the deployed host

### NVIDIA
- Blacklisted by default; unblacklisted only on bare metal via `34-gpu-detect.sh`

### Packages
- `docs/engineering/2026-04-26-Artifact-ENG-001-Packages.md` is the SSOT
- Fenced block format: ` ```packages-<category> `

### Deliverables
Complete replacement files only — no patches, no fragments. Push via `push-to-github.ps1`.

## Build
```bash
just build && just lint
./tests/smoke-test.sh localhost/mios:dev
```

## Memory
Append actions to `.claude/memories/journal.md` with `[AI: Cline]` tag.
Shared scratchpad: `.claude/shared-tmp/`
